{"tid":571670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【經紀收佣90萬】理大學生會涉誇大資金以通過風險評估","createTime":"2018-02-25T00:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T06:27:38.000Z","uid":29314,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3dbbfe9230676f497b682985b58add7a71547b4e","tid":571670,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T00:53:14.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》取得相關保單複本，發現學生會投保時涉誇大擁有的現金，由大約2,000萬元誇大50%至3,000萬元，疑藉此通過風險評估。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此外，臨委會投保時需要申報按年收支，葉報稱學生會每年營運開支約60萬元，被質疑「報細」最少六成。按理大學生會近年收支情況，每年總開支大約為150萬元，主要用作印製學生報、4名全職員薪俸、舉辦活動及補貼福利品等。<br />\n<br />\n有前線保險經紀分析指，若理大學生會如實申報所擁現金，不可能通過風險評估，「cashflow（現金流量）最少要多保費總額一倍，公司都要確保個客有能力、供得起」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">負責處理該保單的經紀在保單生效起計的3個月內，料最少可獲90餘萬元的佣金、季度加年度獎金，「絕對係一張大單」。</span>"},{"pid":"b948ea0a414dd08d1ad798882718318c9a1a06e4","tid":571670,"uid":29314,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T00:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180224/large/1519486174_1fb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180224%2Flarge%2F1519486174_1fb9.jpg&h=9f56827f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前受保人為今屆理大學生會臨時行政委員會主席葉松青。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發發啦，發發啦。"},{"pid":"8bb49e594f551f46c8e28eea73694efdfbafdb2d","tid":571670,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T01:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfb6fc16f995c2e45f7fab8782e80f6f8809416","tid":571670,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T01:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15727125f1a54a11e7974ec35e0255a058986c82","tid":571670,"uid":142212,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"